CodeOrigin
CodeOrigin is a web-based tool that analyzes source code snippets and estimates whether they were written by a human or generated by an AI model. It provides a verdict, confidence score, and short explanations to help users understand the result.
âš ï¸ This project is experimental. Results are probabilistic and should not be used for high-stakes decisions.
